{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-work-template-js","path":"/andcounting/","result":{"data":{"page":{"id":"fa15509d-9893-5769-88ee-69d62ab7c37a","html":"<p class=\"align-center\">\n<a class=\"btn\" href=\"https://github.com/gazpachu/andcounting\" target=\"_blank\">Source code</a>\n</p>\n<p>AndCounting is a collabaration with the entrepreneur and designer Cristina Gaston. The idea was to build an Android app to track multiple projects using stop-watches. The prototype was built using the Cordova platform and allowed the user to start/stop projects, rename them and add new ones to the interface. The report button would send an email with the time logged on each project.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 1536px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 81.6%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"andcounting\"\n        title=\"andcounting\"\n        src=\"/static/1e4a6b61deefe9eb27ddea0cd5ccbea8/6afe2/andcounting.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/1e4a6b61deefe9eb27ddea0cd5ccbea8/d1f95/andcounting.jpg 500w,\n/static/1e4a6b61deefe9eb27ddea0cd5ccbea8/dbdff/andcounting.jpg 1000w,\n/static/1e4a6b61deefe9eb27ddea0cd5ccbea8/6afe2/andcounting.jpg 1536w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1536px) 100vw, 1536px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>","fields":{"prefix":"2013"},"frontmatter":{"title":"AndCounting","categories":"mobile open-source","cover":{"childImageSharp":{"resize":{"src":"/static/f055a0525d2050b3345a4dfc5db9f5c3/f3583/logo.png"}}}}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/andcounting/","source":"wo